title: GoldenEye 007 (Emulator with mouse and keyboard) playthrough -- Part 2
description: Beat the game on 00 Agent difficulty including the two bonus levels. Feels cool to have finally beat it. I enjoyed pretty much all of the game; the last few levels got pretty tough but it was fun. I think I like Perfect Dark more, but this was still cool.
